WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.034 --> 00:00:03.604
TALL-TALE GOLD MEDALIST
RYAN LOCHTE

00:00:03.637 --> 00:00:05.405
HAS STARTED HIS FORGIVENESS TOUR
WITH AN APPEARANCE

00:00:05.439 --> 00:00:07.574
ON THE NEW SEASON
OF <i>DANCING WITH THE STARS.</i>

00:00:07.608 --> 00:00:09.710
IF EVERYONE'S DANCING,
EVERYTHING'S FINE.

00:00:09.743 --> 00:00:12.546
AND THIS TIME,
HE WAS REALLY ALMOST MUGGED.

00:00:12.579 --> 00:00:15.082
-LIAR! -GEORGE STEPHANOPOULOUS:
THERE IT IS.

00:00:15.115 --> 00:00:17.584
PROTESTERS COME ON TO THE STAGE.
THEY'RE GRABBED BY SECURITY.

00:00:17.618 --> 00:00:19.720
SECURITY TAKES HIM DOWN
RIGHT THERE.

00:00:19.753 --> 00:00:21.154
-WHOA.
-(LAUGHTER)

00:00:21.188 --> 00:00:23.757
-YEAH, MAMBO NUMBER FIVE-O.
-(LAUGHTER)

00:00:23.790 --> 00:00:26.560
UH, I WONDER IF THAT PROTESTER
IS GONNA TELL EVERYONE

00:00:26.593 --> 00:00:28.962
THAT HE WAS ALMOST ROBBED. UH...

00:00:28.996 --> 00:00:30.964
-(LAUGHTER)
-COMEDIANS, IT'S BEEN

00:00:30.998 --> 00:00:33.567
NEARLY A WHOLE MONTH SINCE RYAN
LOCHTE'S CONTROVERSIAL RUN-IN

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:36.537
WITH A BRAZILIAN GAS STATION,
AND NOW HE'S DANCING ON THE TV.

00:00:36.570 --> 00:00:38.472
I DON'T KNOW HOW
TO FEEL ABOUT HIM.

00:00:38.505 --> 00:00:40.707
IS IT TIME TO FORGIVE HIM?
DO WE FORGIVE HIM?

00:00:40.741 --> 00:00:42.042
ARE WE NOT OKAY WITH HIM?

00:00:42.075 --> 00:00:43.844
-NO. -NO.
-WHAT DO YOU GUYS THINK?

00:00:43.877 --> 00:00:45.078
-WHOA! -DUDE.
-(LOUD AUDIENCE CHATTER)

00:00:45.112 --> 00:00:46.747
THE AUDIENCE HAS
SOME VERY STRONG OPINIONS.

00:00:46.780 --> 00:00:48.015
VERY STRONG OPINIONS.

00:00:48.048 --> 00:00:50.384
A LOT OF SWEARING IN PORTUGUESE
FROM THE AUDIENCE. UH...

00:00:50.417 --> 00:00:51.552
MOSHE, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

00:00:51.585 --> 00:00:52.986
YEAH, I'M TIRED OF THE ATTITUDE.

00:00:53.020 --> 00:00:55.155
I DON'T THINK HE HAS ANYTHING
TO BE FORGIVEN FOR.

00:00:55.189 --> 00:00:56.890
HE'S A HERO.
HE'S AN AMERICAN.

00:00:56.924 --> 00:00:58.725
THAT'S HOW WE DO IT.

00:00:58.759 --> 00:01:01.862
WE GO TO YOUR COUNTRY,
WIN A GOLD MEDAL, PISS ON IT,

00:01:01.895 --> 00:01:03.764
AND THEN GO DO THE FOXTROT
BACK HOME.

00:01:03.797 --> 00:01:05.132
-HARDWICK: ALL RIGHT.
-(LAUGHTER)

00:01:05.165 --> 00:01:07.935
STRAIGHT UP, I'M TIRED
OF BRAZIL. I'M TIRED OF BRAZIL

00:01:07.968 --> 00:01:10.838
WITH YOUR PERFECT-ASSED WOMEN
AND YOUR PERFECT BEACHES.

00:01:10.871 --> 00:01:12.206
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

00:01:12.239 --> 00:01:14.141
I GREW UP IN THE BAY AREA.
DO YOU KNOW HOW MANY

00:01:14.174 --> 00:01:15.809
CAPOEIRA CIRCLES
I HAD TO PRETEND

00:01:15.843 --> 00:01:17.778
