00:01:17.811 --> 00:01:19.346
-HARDWICK: YEAH.
-(LAUGHTER, APPLAUSE &amp; CHEERING)

00:01:19.379 --> 00:01:20.647
GET BIT, BRAZIL.

00:01:20.681 --> 00:01:23.016
POINTS. YEAH. CHRIS D'ELIA.

00:01:23.050 --> 00:01:25.252
