00:01:54.047 --> 00:01:56.884
FOCUSING ON MAKING AMERICA
GREAT AGAIN,

00:01:56.917 --> 00:01:59.853
LET'S MAKE BRAZIL GREAT
FOR ONCE.

00:01:59.887 --> 00:02:01.488
